Rose Water<br></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-419_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-420_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/mango_lassi_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435909" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/mango_lassi_web.jpg?v=1713435909 1536w" width="600" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="mango lassi web.jpg__PID:1efde24f-9c30-46e8-aeba-ab1cac2d750d" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-421_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-422_ pf-heading-1-h3">Mango Lassi with Rose Water<br></h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-424_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Indulge in the refreshing fusion of flavors with Mango Lassi with Rose Water. This classic Indian beverage combines 500g of natural yogurt, 500g of water, and 250g of mango or mango pulb for a creamy and fruity delight. Sweetened with 2 tbsp of cane sugar and enhanced with 1-3 tbsp of fragrant rose water, each sip is a burst of exotic sweetness. Simply blend all ingredients until smooth, either in a blender or with an immersion blender. For an extra chill on hot days, refrigerate the ingredients beforehand or add a few ice cubes before blending. Treat yourself to this heavenly concoction and experience a taste of tropical paradise.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-426_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_lotion_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435940" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_lotion_web.jpg?v=1713435940 1536w" width="600" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="rose lotion web.jpg__PID:86e8eeba-ab1c-4c2d-b50d-05b9f363be0c" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-427_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-428_ pf-heading-1-h3">Shake Lotion with Rose Water<br></h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-430_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Experience the ultimate hydration and nourishment with a shake lotion infused with luxurious rose water. Crafted with 50 ml of rose hydrolate and 50 ml of nourishing base oil like almond oil, this indulgent blend is poured into a convenient spray bottle for easy application. Shake vigorously before use, then spritz onto the skin for a burst of moisture and care. For an extra touch of luxury, enhance with a few drops of sea buckthorn oil, Rosa rubiginosa, or your favorite essential oil.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-432_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/golden_milk_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435921" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/golden_milk_web.jpg?v=1713435921 1536w" width="600" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="golden milk web.jpg__PID:e24f9c30-86e8-4eba-ab1c-ac2d750d05b9" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-433_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-434_ pf-heading-1-h3">Golden Milk with Rose Water<br></h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-436_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Experience the tranquility and nourishment of golden milk, enhanced with a touch of rose water for an exquisite twist. This harmonious blend, revered for its sattvic and cooling properties, offers a rejuvenating experience for the mind and body. Crafted with care, it features freshly made almond milk infused with curcuma powder and&nbsp; a few crushed pepper corns, delicately scented with rose water, and lightly sweetened with a pinch of sugar. Indulge in this brain rasayana, a tonic for the mind, and savor the soothing flavors that invigorate and refresh with every sip.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-438_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-439_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_lassi_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435931" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_lassi_web.jpg?v=1713435931 1536w" width="602" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="rose lassi web.jpg__PID:9c3086e8-eeba-4b1c-ac2d-750d05b9f363" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-440_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-441_ pf-heading-1-h3">Plain Lassi with Rose Water</h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-443_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Take delight in a refreshing Lassi with the exotic essence of rose water. This harmonious blend combines creamy yogurt, coconut milk and water in similar parts, accented with aromatic cardamom and a hint of sweetness from either sugar or Xylitol. With each spoonful, experience a burst of flavor that tantalizes the taste buds and transports you to a world of culinary bliss. Refreshing and subtly floral, this yogurt delight with rose water is sure to awaken the senses and leave you craving more.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-445_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/sparkling_wine_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435957" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/sparkling_wine_web.jpg?v=1713435957 1536w" width="600" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="sparkling wine web.jpg__PID:ab1cac2d-750d-45b9-b363-be0c62c3cb69" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-446_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-447_ pf-heading-1-h3 pf-hide">Sparkling Wine with Rose Water</h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-449_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Indulge in a delightful twist on traditional sparkling wine with rose water. Simply add 2-3 bursts of fragrant rose water to your glass before pouring in the sparkling wine. Savor the elegant fusion of floral notes and effervescent bubbles for a truly enchanting drinking experience. Cheers to enjoyment and relaxation!</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-451_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_tonic_web_360x.jpg?v=1713435950" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/rose_tonic_web.jpg?v=1713435950 1536w" width="600" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="rose tonic web.jpg__PID:eebaab1c-ac2d-450d-85b9-f363be0c62c3" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-452_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-453_ pf-heading-1-h3">Rose Water as a Skin Tonic</h3><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-455_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Elevate your daily skincare routine with the luxurious touch of rose water. Simply spritz onto cleansed skin for a refreshing and hydrating tonic that rejuvenates and revitalizes. Gentle and soothing, rose water is equally beneficial for scalp and hair care, offering a nourishing treat for locks that shine with natural radiance. Embrace the timeless beauty of rose water and unveil skin and hair that exude health and vitality with each use.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8b01" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fsvrPk eTuePL pf-457_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-eNSrbD jPuwGZ"></div></div></div></div></div><script>
